articles.author: Reuters
articles.title: Australians to reject Indigenous Voice in referendum - final YouGov poll - Reuters.com
articles.description: Australians are set to overwhelmingly say 'No' to a proposal to constitutionally recognise the country's Indigenous people in a referendum on Saturday, one of the final opinion polls ahead of the vote showed.
